Starting this year feeling so grateful for all the wonderful projects, experiences and people that made 2022 such a banner year! Our team is full of bright, brilliant and wonderful people I feel lucky to laugh, work and adventure with! We can’t wait to see what 2023 holds!

We always like to find a spot for a chaise moment in our clients’ homes. Whether you’re reading a book, snuggling up to your kids or propping your legs up for a quiet moment alone, adding a chaise will create the perfect designated corner to meaningful moments at home. 

Sharing @caitlincreerinteriors’ tips on how to make the most of your chaise.
